    <name>ROOT</name>
    <summary>Data Analysis Framework</summary>
    <description>
	<p>
	    ROOT is a framework for data processing, developed at CERN,
            the epicenter of high-energy physics research. It can handle 
            extensive data using the mathematical and statistical methods 
            it provides, along with user-developed routines. The results 
            can be visually presented according to specific needs and 
            exported to various formats such as PDF, PS, PNG, etc.
	</p>
